# Shared tooling (`SourceGeneratorTools.Shared`)

Treat Shared as a **dependency**: change it only when this generator (or other consumers) need a new API. Prefer using existing surface.

## `SourceBuilder`

- Indent-aware emitter (`indent` default `"    "`)
- `CreateBlock("{", "}")` / custom close (e.g. `"};"`) — dispose with `using`
- `CreateLine()` for multi-part signatures with indent restore
- Helpers: `AddAutoGeneratedComment()`, `AddNullableEnable()`, `AddGeneratedCodeAttribute()`
- Never use `Environment.NewLine` in generator code

## `ComparableArray<T>`

- Value-equality list for incremental caching / record equality
- Implicit from `T[]`, `List<T>`, `ImmutableArray<T>`
- Collection expressions via `[CollectionBuilder]` → `ComparableArray.Create`
- Use on any collection stored on pipeline `record`s that participate in equality
